freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: 2/27/21 Bad sore throat, that went into a cold. Runny nose, headache, bad cough, congestion, short of breath on stairs, sleepy. 3/3 & 3/4/21 had a 101.2 degree temp.  Diarrhea yesterday.
March 9, 2021 I had to go to urgent care for supra ventricular tachycardia. Just was a rare event.
